statements: SELECT * FROM wind_turbine_performance_data;
SELECT turbine_id, date, power_output_kW, wind_speed_mph FROM wind_turbine_performance_data;
SELECT turbine_id, power_output_kW FROM wind_turbine_performance_data WHERE wind_speed_mph > 10;
SELECT * FROM wind_turbine_performance_data WHERE date = '2021-10-20';
SELECT turbine_id, power_output_kW FROM wind_turbine_performance_data ORDER BY power_output_kW DESC;
SELECT turbine_id, date, wind_speed_mph, power_output_kW FROM wind_turbine_performance_data;
SELECT * FROM wind_turbine_performance_data ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT AVG(wind_speed_mph) AS avg_wind_speed FROM wind_turbine_performance_data;
SELECT SUM(power_output_kW), date FROM wind_turbine_performance_data GROUP BY date HAVING SUM(power_output_kW) > 1000;
SELECT turbine_id, date, wind_speed_mph, power_output_kW FROM wind_turbine_performance_data WHERE wind_speed_mph > 20 ORDER BY power_output_kW DESC;
SELECT * FROM wind_turbine_performance_data WHERE location = 'New York';
SELECT turbine_id, wind_speed FROM wind_turbine_performance_data WHERE power_generated > 1000;
SELECT power_generated, location FROM wind_turbine_performance_data ORDER BY power_generated DESC;
SELECT turbine_id, location, wind_speed, power_generated FROM wind_turbine_performance_data WHERE wind_speed BETWEEN 20 AND 30;
SELECT * FROM maintenance_logs WHERE maintenance_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-06-30';
SELECT * FROM wind_turbine_performance_data WHERE wind_speed > 10 ORDER BY power_generated DESC;
SELECT turbine_id, location, SUM(power_generated) AS total_power_generated FROM wind_turbine_performance_data GROUP BY turbine_id, location;
SELECT wt.turbine_id, wt.location, ml.maintenance_date, ml.maintenance_details FROM wind_turbine_performance_data wt LEFT JOIN maintenance_logs ml ON wt.turbine_id = ml.turbine_id;
SELECT location, AVG(power_generated) AS avg_power FROM wind_turbine_performance_data GROUP BY location HAVING avg_power > 50;
SELECT turbine_id, location, wind_speed, power_generated FROM wind_turbine_performance_data WHERE location LIKE 'North%' ORDER BY turbine_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM WindTurbine;
SELECT turbine_name, location FROM WindTurbine WHERE rated_capacity > 100;
SELECT turbine_name, rated_capacity, location FROM WindTurbine WHERE turbine_id = 3;
SELECT * FROM TurbineData WHERE power_generated > 500 AND efficiency < 0.8;
SELECT turbine_id, maintenance_type, maintenance_details FROM MaintenanceLog ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT turbine_id, turbine_name, rated_capacity FROM WindTurbine WHERE rated_capacity > 1000 ORDER BY rated_capacity DESC;
SELECT turbine_id, location FROM WindTurbine WHERE location LIKE 'USA%' ORDER BY turbine_id ASC;
SELECT turbine_id, timestamp, wind_speed, power_generated FROM TurbineData WHERE wind_speed > 10 AND power_generated > 100 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT turbine_id, maintenance_type, maintenance_details FROM MaintenanceLog WHERE maintenance_type = 'Preventive Maintenance' ORDER BY turbine_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM WindTurbine JOIN TurbineData ON WindTurbine.turbine_id = TurbineData.turbine_id WHERE wind_speed > 15 AND power_generated > 200 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM WindTurbine;
SELECT turbine_name, power_output FROM WindTurbine WHERE location = 'New York';
SELECT id, location, last_maintenance_date FROM WindTurbine ORDER BY last_maintenance_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM WindTurbine WHERE power_output > 5000 ORDER BY location DESC;
SELECT turbine_name, power_output FROM WindTurbine WHERE last_maintenance_date < '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM WindTurbine WHERE location = 'New York' ORDER BY last_maintenance_date DESC
SELECT id, turbine_name, power_output FROM WindTurbine WHERE power_output > 1000 ORDER BY turbine_name ASC
SELECT turbine_name, location FROM WindTurbine WHERE last_maintenance_date < '2022-01-01' ORDER BY location, turbine_name
SELECT id, turbine_name, power_output FROM WindTurbine WHERE power_output BETWEEN 500 AND 2000 ORDER BY id DESC
SELECT * FROM WindTurbine WHERE location = 'California' AND power_output > 1500 ORDER BY location, power_output DESC
SELECT * FROM WindTurbineData
SELECT turbine_name, location FROM WindTurbineData ORDER BY location ASC
SELECT power_output, wind_speed FROM WindTurbineData WHERE wind_speed > 10
SELECT * FROM MaintenanceRecords WHERE maintenance_type = 'scheduled'
SELECT location_name, region, country FROM TurbineLocations
SELECT * FROM WindTurbineData WHERE wind_speed > 10 ORDER BY power_output DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT location, AVG(wind_speed) AS avg_wind_speed FROM WeatherData GROUP BY location HAVING avg_wind_speed > 15 ORDER BY avg_wind_speed DESC;

SELECT t.turbine_name, m.maintenance_type, m.maintenance_date FROM WindTurbineData t JOIN MaintenanceRecords m ON t.id = m.turbine_id WHERE m.maintenance_type = 'inspection' ORDER BY m.maintenance_date ASC;
SELECT location_name, COUNT(*) AS number_of_turbines FROM TurbineLocations GROUP BY location_name ORDER BY number_of_turbines DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT w.location, w.temperature, th.health_status FROM WeatherData w JOIN TurbineHealth th ON w.location = th.health_status WHERE w.temperature < 0 ORDER BY w.temperature ASC;
